/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aca99715e84577682ea024411980eac704205542","tid":359291,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T16:02:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好鍾意呀，較到燈暗暗地聽靜既歌，好舒服<br />\n可惜第日要返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n放假前一晚必須試<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2490f7e90b6f52e2833530984d87109935a76a49","tid":359291,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T16:03:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想像下自己係果架已經開走嘅電<br />\n想像下自己係大去不復返嘅潮浪<br />\n可以隨處流浪 想到哪方便哪方<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日幻想自己係一隻羊<br />\n係大牧場食草，柯屎，訓覺<br />\n咩都唔洗諗<br />\n得閒有人剃，真係好撚爽</blockquote><br />\n羊好咩<br />\n想做一隻飛鳥<br />\n就算餓死起碼都係天空翱翔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26705e5d773d70f92aabe7509c357e3d8af8bede","tid":359291,"uid":13859,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T16:05:32.000Z","msg":"秋天淩晨真係好正<br />\n淩晨+秋天浸味<br />\n咩回憶都出哂黎 舒服到起雞皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71e4ce3031f974eafd2b8ae1daad5e942f1b1609","tid":359291,"uid":68375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T16:05:52.000Z","msg":"屋企面海，一到夜晚會行出露台吹海風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1f8eb56107022a08d670024b3a3d324749bae86","tid":359291,"uid":6866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-14T16:07:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想像下自己係果架已經開走嘅電<br />\n想像下自己係大去不復返嘅潮浪<br />\n可以隨處流浪 想到哪方便哪方<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我成日幻想自己係一隻羊<br />\n係大牧場食草，柯屎，訓覺<br />\n咩都唔洗諗<br />\n得閒有人剃，真係好撚爽</blockquote><br />\n羊好咩<br />\n想做一隻飛鳥<br />\n就算餓死起碼都係天空翱翔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"